'''Esther M. Friesner''' is a science fiction author of novels and short stories. She won the [[Wikipedia:Nebula Award for Best Short Story|Nebula Award for Best Short Story]] in both [[1995]] and [[1996]]. Also in 1996, she wrote "[[That's Entertainment: The Tale of Salacious Crumb]]," a short story for the ''[[Tales from Jabba's Palace]]'' anthology.

